dkid-single/1112936265|title=Highschool Never Ends (feat. Woodkid) - Single by Mykki Blanco on Apple Music|work=iTunes Store|accessdate=16 October 2018}}</ref><br>{{small|([[Mykki Blanco]] featuring Woodkid)}}\n| 2016\n| ''[[Mykki]]''\n|}\n\n====Notes====\n{{notelist-ua}}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!align=\"centre\"|Year\n!align=\"left\"|Song\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2011\n|align=\"left\"|\"Iron\"<ref name=AgynessDeyn />\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2012\n|align=\"left\"|\"Run Boy Run\"\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2013\n|align=\"left\"|\"I Love You\"\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2014\n|align=\"left\"|\"The Golden Age\"\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2016\n|align=\"left\"|\"Land of All\"\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2020\n|align=\"left\"|\"Goliath\"\n|}\n\n==Videography as director==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!align=\"centre\"|Year\n!align=\"left\"|Artist(s)\n!align=\"left\"|Song\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2008\n|align=\"left\"|[[Yelle]]\n|align=\"left\"|\"Ce Jeu\"<ref Name=Yelle>{{cite web |url=http://auralstates.com/2008/10/interview-yelle.html|title=Interview with Yelle|date=June 8, 2011|publisher=Aural States|accessdate=June 8, 2011}}</ref>\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2009\n|align=\"left\"|[[Nolwenn Leroy]]\n|align=\"left\"|\"Faut-il, faut-il pas ?\"<ref Name=NolwennLeroy>{{cite web |url=http://www.elle.fr/Loisirs/Musique/Dossiers/Rencontre-avec-Nolwenn-et-son-Cheshire-Cat-1090289#|title=Interview with Nolwenn Leroy|publisher=elle.fr (in French)|accessdate=November 6, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2009\n|align=\"left\"|[[Moby]]\n|align=\"left\"|\"[[Mistake (Moby song)|Mistake]]\"\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2010\n|align=\"left\"|[[Mystery Jets]]\n|align=\"left\"|\"Dreaming of Another World\"\n|-\n|align=\"centre\"|2010\n|align=\"left\"|[[Katy Perry]]\n|align=\"left\"|\"[[Teenage Dream (Katy Perry song)|Teenage Dream]]\"<ref Name=TeenageDream>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1643826/katy-perry-talks-gorgeous-video-teenage-dream.jhtml|title=Katy Perry Talks 'Gorg