bc1c\u2026'\ubc31\uc77c\uc758 \ub0ad\uad70\ub2d8' \ud558\ucc28|url=http://www.nocutnews.co.kr/news/4972549|accessdate=May 21, 2018|work=Nocut News|date=May 21, 2018|language=ko}}</ref> Yoon was called in the next day to the police station where the police determined that his blood alcohol content was 0.140 percent at the time of the accident.<ref>{{cite news|last=Sung|first=Ji-eun|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3048404|title=Yoon Tae-young charged for drunk driving|date=May 22, 2018|website=Korea JoongAng Daily|accessdate=May 22, 2018}}</ref> The police suspended his licenses, and after the news broke out, producers of the then upcoming TV series ''[[100 Days My Prince]]'' announced their intent to replace him with another actor.<ref>{{cite news|last=Kim|first=Mi-ri|script-title=ko:'\ubc31\uc77c\uc758 \ub0ad\uad70\ub2d8' \uce21 \"\uc724\ud0dc\uc601 \ud558\ucc28, \ub300\uccb4 \ubc30\uc6b0 \ud604\uc7ac \ubbf8\uc815\" [\uacf5\uc2dd\uc785\uc7a5 \uc804\ubb38]|url=http://www.mydaily.co.kr/new_yk/html/read.php?newsid=201805210210915001&ext=na|accessdate=May 21, 2018|work=My Daily|date=May 21, 2018|language=ko}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Lee|first=Suh-yoon|title=Actor Yoon kicked out of K-drama for drunk driving|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/art/2018/05/398_249337.html|accessdate=May 22, 2018|work=The Korea Times|date=May 21, 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Television series==\n*''[[Local Hero (TV series)|Local Hero]]'' (OCN, 2016)\n*''[[Drama City|Drama Special]]'' \"The Final Puzzle\" (KBS2, 2014)\n*''[[Diary of a Night Watchman]]'' (MBC, 2014)\n*''[[The King's Daughter, Soo Baek-hyang]]'' (MBC, 2013-2014)\n*''Midnight Hospital'' (MBC, 2011)\n*''Strike Love'' (MBC, 2009)\n*''[[The Legend (TV series)|The Legend]]'' (MBC, 2007)\n*''Special Crime Investigation: Murder in the Blue House'' (KBS2, 2006)\n*''Pearl Necklace'' (KBS2, 2003-2004)\n*''On the Prairie'' <!--aka Over the Green Fields--> (KBS2, 2003)\n*''Nothing Better and Nothing Worse'' 